  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "</b> </i>] [<i>Permits the Department of Human Services to place an Indian child in an out-of-state placement without requiring the placement to be licensed by or under contract with the department or to be a qualified residential treatment facility if certain standards are met.</i>] <b>Permits</b> <b>the Department of Human Services to make certain out of state placements of children in specified circumstances.</b> Declares an emergency, effective on passage."
    }
